================================== HADOOP:SETUP =======================
1) Download the following file:
   - hadoop.rpm
   - java.rpm

2) Installed the software:
    rpm -ivh jdk.rpm
    rpm -ivh hadoop.rpm --force

3) Check software installed successfully using cmd:
    hadoop version
    java -version 

4)===namenode setup
    cd /etc/hadoop/

    vim hdfs-site.xml

<configuration>
<property>
<name>dfs.name.dir</name>
<value>/nn</value>
</property>
</configuration>    

    hadoop namenode -format

    vim core-site.xml

<configuration>
<property>
<name>fs.default.name</name>
<value>hdfs://0.0.0.0:9001</value>
</property>
</configuration>

    hadoop-daemon.sh start namenode
    jps (if nanenode successfuly made)
    netstat  -tnlp  | grep java

===datanode setup

 cd /etc/hadoop/

       vim hdfs-site.xml

